ddot.it/this ..format.. format:trix
ddot.it/this ..content.. TriX document with a single named <graph> holding triples generated by the Aperture semantic-desktop crawler over a local file tree. Uses <uri>, <plainLiteral> and xsd:dateTime <typedLiteral> objects.
ddot.it/this ..tests.. TriX parsing of a named graph with mixed object kinds: <uri>, <plainLiteral> and xsd:dateTime <typedLiteral>.
